## Glossary [/posts]

### List all post [GET /{?filter,skip,limit,fields,sort}]

Get all the posts

+ Parameters
    + skip : 0(optional, string) ... The number of documents to be skipped.
    + limit : 10 (optional, number) ... Limits the number of doocument to be retrieved
    + fields : "name description" (optional, string) ... Space or Comma separated field names to be supplied to retrieve those fields of the documents
    + filter : "{'active':true}" (optional, string) ... Stringified Object having keys and values based on which the search is to be filterd.
    + sort : "created_at" (optional, string) ... The order in which the result is to be fetched i.e., Ascending or Descending order

+ Request (application/json; charset=utf-8)


+ Response 200

    + Body

