### Post the glossary [POST]

Post the glossary with following body parameters
+ title (string) - Title
+ content (string) - Content of the post
+ summary (string) - Summary
+ status (string) - draft, pending, publish, trash
+ slug (string) - Slug
+ tags (array) - array of tags
+ owner (object)
+ attachments (array) - array of attachments having 'url' and 'is_cover' as keys
+ post_type (string) - bjglossary, bjtv, article

+ Request (application/json; charset=utf-8)

